---
title: Garlicky Shrimp with Roasted Potatoes and Walnut-Parsley Pesto
description: Garlic and shrimp aren't the only stars for dinner tonight! We've paired them with a DIY walnut and parsley pesto, crisp spinach and roasted potatoes. Your taste buds will be singing on centre stage!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crevettes-a-lail-d189d96b.jpg
